Onboarding Root
1. Create Project: everarcade new --template arena --name my-arena
2. Build Project: everarcade build --project my-arena
3. Run Project: node my-arena/src/game.js
4. Deploy Project: everarcade deploy --project my-arena --target local
5. Publish Project: everarcade publish --project my-arena --channel creator-testnet
Goal: first game in under one hour.
